Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff1,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫皆城总士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你听到这段话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该已经不在这个世界上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:25.92,type1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\blur1}2150年6月25日 夏威夷生存圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对人类而言 22世纪成为了战争的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:35.64,type1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur1}人类军波莉亚芙运输基地 上空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:35.64,type1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\fs30\pos(582,565)}Poliʻahu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\fad(1000,0)}注：夏威夷神话中的四位雪之女神之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自遥远太空的未知生物 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们拥有人类所无法理解的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现在这个星球上已有40年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大半个世界都沦为了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已进入战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60秒后降落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵循作战计划 迅速投身前线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是经过严格训练筛选出的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你们一起战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到十分骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:01:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二号机 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比报告上写的还糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Second machine Olympia-Angels, landing check
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(640,655)}二号机 Olympia-Angels着陆确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要像哥哥这样战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(685,655)\fs30}Billy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四号机 出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对Festum专用思维控制体感操纵式载人兵器法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1037,655)\fs30}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有被选中的人才能操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的底牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Type1 Type2 Type3 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意Type4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内置敌人的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其力量为人类所用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们早就灭亡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便还远远无法取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也用它争取到了萌生希望的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒纳凯阿巡逻基地崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(518,655)}Mauna Kea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注：夏威夷岛上的五座火山之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部机能…都被敌人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧引导平民疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有部队集结到北部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一防卫队被歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距本岛最终防卫线还有两公里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(455,655)}Big Island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃吧 那雷恩将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(643,655)}Narain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是太平洋圈最大的运输基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦这里被攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数百万人都会饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么都要守住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们学习了之前不屑一顾的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习了人类是如何自保的吗 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能登机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们可都逼到眼前了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急 马上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒纳凯阿不会有事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部发布交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布对象为本岛全域！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总部指挥的空袭部队正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我接新联合国总部！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的名义发布攻击中止令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有战友在战斗啊！而且还有好几万平民！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交战规定α必须遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剥夺沃尔特少校的职权 即刻逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,655)\fs30}Walter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那雷恩将军命令中止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入坐标 进入攻击态势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都去搜寻生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我攻击了友军…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受不了了…有人活着吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我们赢不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 究竟是为了什么 为了什么而战的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旷日持久的战争让世界凋敝不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能够理解彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争是否也就能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样渺茫的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在世界的角落中等待破土
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是日本在战乱中毁灭之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为传承和平这一文化而建造的人工岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我曾经的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地区大赛就快到了 鼓起干劲来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香明白 要老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美香美香 你可别出全力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近藤医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 咲良
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续继续…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到她就想起过去的一骑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 回去的时候上一骑那儿吃顿饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 你讨厌我做的饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}堂马广登特别节目 追踪神秘巨型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢广登是做了多少节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹也是太有奉陪精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 无聊透顶 天气还热
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我想去Alvis上班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别光学打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也得继承岛上的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你好 里奈前辈…哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事 镝木？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？呃 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你不是昨天就买过这本了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？那个…这本是收藏用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说镝木 你是学生会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道买漫画 七夕祭典的准备都做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这个…里奈前辈不在讨论就没法进行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够不争气的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然下次到一骑前辈那里一起讨论？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 里奈前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我在上班啊 怎么可能会有空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也…是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ改 上臂引擎安装完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进行FTP试验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接确认完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越熟练了呢 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(788,655)\fs30}Kanon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了妈妈的教导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里可是职员兼教官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 羽佐间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 出去吃个饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天待在这儿要闷出病来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是想去一骑那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒无所谓…去哪里都成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不希望再有人驾驶了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然又要把它组装起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到卡农会去学工程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小年纪技术却很了得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是想做你徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干脆退休算了 毕竟还得画这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是驾驶员培养教材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊 西尾老师开口的事没法推托啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该吃饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就老规矩 去吃咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗 会赶不上午市的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有问题的 让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是御门的 东西我搬到里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 老爸教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说这个 一骑哥 有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 你来得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午的研究收工了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子准备还没好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过会儿再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来吧 吃饭是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是晖咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 新品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不是 不过菜名加上厨师的名字是这里的规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如一骑咖喱什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沟口先生擅自加的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我很尊敬一骑前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见和沟口先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我还以为能和远见前辈一起工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows呼叫控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已捕捉到不明机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}unknown follow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入自动瞄准程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘有一手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这招怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定目标 发射导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}Target Fox-One
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你超前了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}run out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能因为自己飞得快就把敌人给超了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 坐在大飞机上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽她啊 最近总是这样净跟幻想中的朋友说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因为没有同龄的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得不用太担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子很感性 所以我就是放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真矢姐姐也坐在飞机上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快了呢 艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,655)\fs30}Emery
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡农是蜜瓜雪顶和…请用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么啊 我可没点这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费赠送
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你常常来光顾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是不…讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见学航空 卡农学工科 剑司学医疗 要投身教育
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都决定了各自的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士你搞研究吗 感觉挺合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？在咖啡馆当厨师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 还挺合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想让当年的王牌驾驶员的宝贵经验发挥余热
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当教官也是个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些痕迹 不开法芙娜了也还是留着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是尼伯龙根连接导致的小规模同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(433,655)\fs30}Nibelungen
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会找到治疗方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始学些什么 做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后这些事却以未完成收场 我不喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这样的吗 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是有希望恢复的 别太悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有三年…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么长的时间 足够我做心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何况现在眼睛也能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是和平安稳的 重要的伙伴生活的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我会一直在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你一直保护着这个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 怎么了 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对什么东西起反应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫CDC 不明机体接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注：CDC=作战指挥中心(Combat Direction Center)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,90秒后将到达防护罩外沿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,655)\fs30}Shield Line
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标已进入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,655)\fs30}Target Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标情报入库 比对结果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,655)\fs30}Target Merge
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.21,0:18:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C-300 Super Galaxy 目标为人类军大型运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感应到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一个十分美丽的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 艾梅莉好像也感应到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让我们见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫CDC 紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Arrows 维持距离跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(715,655)\fs30}Follow Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汇报情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到训练中的红隼战斗机报告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,655)\fs30}Kestrel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军运输机正在靠近 紧急事态发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于防护罩外确认到质量不明的回转体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(901,655)}worm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门系统没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,655)\fs30}Shlomo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有机库启动迎击态势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(560,655)\fs30}burg
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1 第2重力波防护罩已展开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,655)\fs30}Welle Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航路不变 法芙娜准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动手 敌人还没有发现我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军只是在一味地逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要放他们离开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住区传来通信请求 是日野家发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 美羽她突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 她说请救助那架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}拜托了 妈妈 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}别担心 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不要激动 正在帮你问了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}今天有工作的人员请立即进入应急态势
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}各位岛民请勿外出 等待最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}随着应急体制的启动 第一……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}防御幕墙已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1\pos(575,60)\fs30}waffeladen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}向岛防卫线 刚瑠岛控制区……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(735,200)\frz22\frx12\fry-12}出击要求播报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕果然棒透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说彗 同样的杂志你昨天就买过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改成出击要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这段视频的灯光打得一般般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别录太多版啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说要实战 我们是不是也能驾驶法芙娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连接测试都没做过就上？应该只是观战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 我都还没像广登前辈那样做好头盔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那东西根本不需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的前辈留给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可得好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广登前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把护身头盔给她没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我们能开法芙娜的时间也没剩几年了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趁现在让她继承了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能主动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门系统发出应答 敌人很可能在200秒内实体化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向50° 减速航行 防护罩部分解除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红隼战斗机引导运输机降落到海面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CDC呼叫Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请按流程开始引导运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(802,655)}track
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伪装镜面 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入代码 伪装镜面解除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是岛 真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始毕业考试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫飞行中的C-300
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是FA3 代号Arrows 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是C-300 代号Cetus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隶属人类军南亚舰队特殊航空连队珀耳修斯中队
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(905,655)\fs30}Perseus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}注：希腊神话中宙斯的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫Cetus 请遵循引导
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫Arrows 我方将全面听从指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换 请你转告你的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的愿望是让彼此的希望相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用无数牺牲换来的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事物是不惜失去它也要追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未知的希望与新的战斗齐至的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.42,0:24:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最后的时光拉开了帷幕
